KOLCHAK: THE NIGHT STALKER -1x15- CHOPPER (1/31/1975) 

The strange disappearance of an antique motorcycle is the first sign of trouble. Kolchak discovers the connection between the victims and their killer, but the skeptical police won&#039;t listen to his theory. Kolchak must find a way to stop the killings, and discovers that disturbing the dead is not always wise...
